---
import Base from "../layouts/base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Discovery-as-a-Service"
  description="A faster, easier way to buy strategic insight, judgment and clarity — without the friction."
  type="WebPage"
  canonicalURL="https://getclarity.win/discovery-as-a-service"
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Discovery-as-a-Service</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
      A faster, more flexible alternative to consultants, contractors, and
      agencies.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 1: What is it? -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 mb-20 text-left">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">What is Discovery-as-a-Service?</h2>
    <p class="text-lg mb-4">
      It's simple. You get access to an experienced thinking partner, on demand.
      We help you make better decisions, faster, without spinning up a project.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg">
      No scope. No bloat. Just enough structure to act with confidence when it
      counts.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: The Grand Slam Offer -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 mb-20">
    <div
      class="p-8 rounded-xl bg-[#75C1E8] dark:bg-[#429EDB] text-white text-center"
    >
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">What You Get, All at Once</h3>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col h-full p-6 rounded-lg text-left items-center justify-center mb-12"
      >
        <ul
          class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm md:text-base list-disc list-outside"
        >
          <li>Senior strategic partner (on tap, not on payroll)</li>
          <li>No setup fees. No scope creep. No delays</li>
          <li>Clarity Sessions, Briefs and Radars within days</li>
          <li>Direct answers. Decision-ready input. Ongoing support</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold">
        From £4,999/month. No contracts. Cancel anytime.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3: Compared to Old Models -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 mb-20 text-left">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
          Why Not Contractors, Consultants, or Agencies?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          Contractors mean headcount. Agencies mean overhead. Consultants mean
          delay.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          Clarity. delivers senior-level thinking on tap. No briefing decks. No
          middle layers. Just results.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[#429EDB]/10 dark:bg-[#1F78C1]/20">
        <p class="font-semibold mb-2 text-center">What You Avoid:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 text-left text-lg space-y-2">
          <li>Time wasted on outputs you don't need</li>
          <li>Delays waiting on contracts or teams</li>
          <li>Being sold work you don't need</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4: Who it's for -->
  <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 mb-20 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Is This Right for You?</h2>
    <p class="text-lg mb-4">
      Discovery-as-a-Service is made for Heads of Product, Programme Directors,
      Digital Leaders who need to stay in motion while making strategic
      decisions.
    </p>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col h-full p-6 rounded-lg text-left items-center justify-center mb-12"
    >
      <ul
        class="grid md:grid-cols-1 gap-4 text-sm md:text-lg list-disc list-outside"
      >
        <li>You're moving fast and can't afford to stall</li>
        <li>You're accountable but alignment is missing</li>
        <li>You need experienced judgment, not a team to manage</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5: CTA -->
  <section class="text-center my-12">
    <h2 class="text-xl mb-4 font-semibold">
      Ready to make faster, better decisions?
    </h2>
    <a
      href="/support-plans"
      class="inline-block bg-[#429EDB] text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-[#1F78C1] transition"
    >
      Explore Support Plans
    </a>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      No contracts. No pressure. Just smart support.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
